 <span data-ttu-id="53c25-394">如需有關如何將值儲存在工作階段狀態的資訊，請參閱[如何： 將值儲存在工作階段狀態](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/a6cb2e3a-df49-4b12-9d9a-eed45541c165)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="53c25-394">For information about how to save values in session state, see [How to: Save Values in Session State](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/a6cb2e3a-df49-4b12-9d9a-eed45541c165).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="53c25-395">如需如何從工作階段狀態中讀取值的資訊，請參閱[如何： 從工作階段狀態的讀取值](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/2ef449bc-5c17-4785-b7cf-378c601af8f5)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="53c25-395">For information about how to read values from session state, see [How to: Read Values from Session State](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/2ef449bc-5c17-4785-b7cf-378c601af8f5).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="53c25-396">下列範例示範如何將值儲存在工作階段狀態及如何讀取工作階段狀態的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="53c25-396">The following examples show how to save values in session state and how to read values from session state.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="53c25-397">這些範例需要：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="53c25-397">These examples require:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="53c25-398">ASP.NET 應用程式已啟用的工作階段狀態。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="53c25-398">An ASP.NET application that has session state enabled.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="53c25-399">Web Form 頁面類別具有存取權<xref:System.Web.UI.Page.Session%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性或具有存取權的任何類別<xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Current%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="53c25-399">A Web Forms page class that has access to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.Session%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property, or any class that has access to the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Current%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
string firstName = "Jeff";  
string lastName = "Smith";  
string city = "Seattle";  
  
// Save to session state in a Web Forms page class.  
Session["FirstName"] = firstName;  
Session["LastName"] = lastName;  
Session["City"] = city;  
  
// Read from session state in a Web Forms page class.  
firstName = (string)(Session["FirstName"]);  
lastName = (string)(Session["LastName"]);  
city = (string)(Session["City"]);  
  
// Outside of Web Forms page class, use HttpContext.Current.  
HttpContext context = HttpContext.Current;  
context.Session["FirstName"] = firstName;  
firstName = (string)(context.Session["FirstName"]);  
  
```  
  
```vb  
Dim firstName As String = "Jeff"  
Dim lastName As String = "Smith"  
Dim city As String = "Seattle"  
  
' Save to session state in a Web Forms page class.  
Session("FirstName") = firstName  
Session("LastName") = lastName  
Session("City") = city  
  
' Read from session state in a Web Forms page class.  
firstName = DirectCast(Session("FirstName"), String)  
lastName = DirectCast(Session("LastName"), String)  
city = DirectCast(Session("City"), String)  
  
' Outside of Web Forms page class, use HttpContext.Current.  
Dim context As HttpContext = HttpContext.Current  
context.Session("FirstName") = firstName  
firstName = DirectCast(context.Session("FirstName"), String)  
  
```
